msgid "# triton.language.debug_barrier"
msgstr "# triton.language.debug_barrier"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/debug_barrier.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/debug_barrier.md:4
msgid "`debug_barrier` 插入一条屏障指令，用于在调试时同步块中的所有线程，确保线程间的执行顺序。在同一块中的所有其他线程也到达该点之前，任何线程都不会继续执行该调用。"
msgstr "`debug_barrier` inserts a barrier instruction used to synchronize all threads in a block during debugging, ensuring the execution order among threads. No thread will continue executing past this call until all other threads in the same block have also reached this point."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Compiler_Hint_Ops/debug_barrier.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.debug_barrier(_semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

